---
title: Harvest Chicken & Spinach Salad with Feta Elevated Dinners, Impressively Easy
description: You asked, and we delivered: It’s time for another stellar entry in our Fast & Fresh family of 15-minute recipes! This simple, hearty salad is packed with comforting fall flavors and crisp textures for a light, satisfying meal. Start by seasoning chicken cutlets with our bold, savory steak seasoning, then searing them to a deep golden brown. Nestle it atop a vibrant salad of fresh spinach tossed with juicy sliced pear, tangy-sweet dried cranberries, nutty pecans, crispy croutons, and tangy feta in a creamy balsamic dressing.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/652e9c930adad327d2408da0-a65b94a3.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/652e9c930adad327d2408da0.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/harvest-chicken-spinach-salad-with-feta-652e9c930adad327d2408da0
time required: 15 minutes
cuisine: North America
nutrition:
  calories: 680 kcal
  fat: 35 g
